compiz-fusion sequence:


1) compiz

2) compiz-bcop

3) protobuf (optional but recommended)

4) libcompizconfig (protobuf)

5) compizconfig-python (libcompizconfig)

6) ccsm (libsexy, sexy-python)

7) simple-ccsm (ccsm, libsexy, sexy-python)

8) compiz-plugins-main

9) compiz-plugins-extra (compiz-plugins-main - optional)

10) compiz-plugins-unsupported (compiz-plugins-main - optional)

11) compizconfig-backend-kconfig4 (libcompizconfig - optional)

12) emerald (compiz - optional)

13) emerald-themes (emerald - optional)

14) fusion-icon (optional)
